Backlighting Is the Best

00:03:15.400 --> 00:03:18.550
We're borrowing our father's DSLR for our camera.

00:03:18.750 --> 00:03:20.300
It looks so cool!

00:03:20.930 --> 00:03:22.950
Is your dad a professional photographer?

00:03:22.950 --> 00:03:25.300
No, photography is just his hobby.

00:03:25.300 --> 00:03:26.720
So mature!

00:03:26.940 --> 00:03:30.890
This camera is great because you don't have to change the lens!

00:03:31.160 --> 00:03:33.810
Do you usually switch out lenses?

00:03:34.110 --> 00:03:36.190
You can change them to fit your preferences.

00:03:36.190 --> 00:03:41.070
Fisheye Lens Normal Lens Telephoto Lens

00:03:36.540 --> 00:03:38.070
If you change out the lens,

00:03:38.070 --> 00:03:41.070
you get different results, even when taking the same photo. It's a lot of fun!

00:03:41.720 --> 00:03:42.470
Question.

00:03:42.470 --> 00:03:44.550
Uh, yes? G-Gojo-san...

00:03:44.550 --> 00:03:48.080
Is there a big difference compared to shooting with a smartphone?

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:49.280
Yes.

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:53.170
The camera gives you a higher resolution and there's so much more you can do.

00:03:53.720 --> 00:03:56.170
For example, if you take a photo with flowers in the background...

00:03:56.800 --> 00:04:00.880
You can blur the background to make the cosplayer stand out more.

00:04:01.050 --> 00:04:04.890
Or you can blur the foreground and make the whole photo look soft.

00:04:05.130 --> 00:04:07.240
If you play with the shutter speed,

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:10.020
you can take a photo with falling petals without them being blurry.

00:04:10.220 --> 00:04:11.630
That's amazing!

00:04:11.630 --> 00:04:14.030
Aw, man... That sounds like so much fun.

00:04:14.030 --> 00:04:15.020
Yes!

00:04:15.020 --> 00:04:16.820
Whenever a picture turns out how I want,

00:04:16.820 --> 00:04:18.860
or I coincidentally get a great expression,

00:04:18.860 --> 00:04:20.440
it makes me so happy.

00:04:21.480 --> 00:04:25.950
It makes me want to become better so I can take even better photos.

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:28.200
Plus, you're taking pics of the Juju-sama!

00:04:28.200 --> 00:04:29.810
You must be hyped!

00:04:29.810 --> 00:04:30.920
Yes.

00:04:30.920 --> 00:04:34.020
By the way, you don't cosplay, Shinju-chan?

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:38.840
Doesn't seeing so many cosplayers make you want to try it?

00:04:39.240 --> 00:04:41.460
And you're like, "They're so cute! That seems super fun!"

00:04:41.780 --> 00:04:43.820
"So maybe I'll try it, too," yeah?

00:04:46.130 --> 00:04:47.640
Me...?

00:04:48.100 --> 00:04:49.310
Did you want to cosplay, too?

00:04:51.200 --> 00:04:52.330
No...

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:53.810
Not at all.

00:04:53.810 --> 00:04:55.430
It doesn't make me want to do it.

00:04:55.430 --> 00:04:57.650
I just like taking pictures of my sister.

00:04:57.650 --> 00:04:59.320
I'm not going to cosplay...

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:01.700
Oh, I see.

00:05:01.700 --> 00:05:02.430
Yes.

00:05:03.440 --> 00:05:06.220
Hey, Shinju-chan. Can I touch your camera?

00:05:06.220 --> 00:05:07.230
Sure.

00:05:07.700 --> 00:05:09.330
Cameras are so cool!

00:05:09.330 --> 00:05:13.080
I wanna take a photo with a neat background bokeh effect!

00:05:13.350 --> 00:05:15.400
I'm totally saving up so I can buy one.

00:05:15.400 --> 00:05:19.040
How much do DSLRs cost?

00:05:19.040 --> 00:05:22.550
Tsaica camera shop (All 5 Shops)

00:05:20.230 --> 00:05:21.160
Oh, here we go.

00:05:23.610 --> 00:05:24.350
Huh?

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:25.920
camera shop (All 5 Shops)

00:05:25.090 --> 00:05:28.350
Huh?!

00:05:25.920 --> 00:05:26.680
Monochrome (All 7 Shops)

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:27.720
(All 7 Shops)

00:05:27.800 --> 00:05:28.720
(Lens Sold Separately)

00:05:28.900 --> 00:05:31.000
Lens sold separately?!

00:05:31.940 --> 00:05:32.890
Dude, you're so loud!

00:05:33.190 --> 00:05:36.350
If you add a tripod, flash, and the rest of the equipment, it costs even more.

00:05:37.230 --> 00:05:39.060
10,000 Yen

00:05:40.580 --> 00:05:42.710
Your mind's totally blown, Gojo-kun.

00:05:43.690 --> 00:05:49.220
I can't believe the cameras everyone had at the other day's event were so expensive...

00:05:49.220 --> 00:05:50.660
Crazy, am I right?

00:05:51.080 --> 00:05:55.150
Well, I guess we'll just have to keep using our smartphones until I save up.

00:05:55.150 --> 00:05:55.840
Ah...

00:05:55.840 --> 00:05:59.000
Kitagawa-san's not even hesitating on buying one.

00:05:59.280 --> 00:06:03.050
There are all kinds of cameras, so make sure you buy one that's in your budget.

00:06:04.260 --> 00:06:07.440
By the way, we're going to scout for shooting locations,
Thank you very much.

00:06:07.460 --> 00:06:09.520
but do you two want to come along?

00:06:09.520 --> 00:06:11.600
It's the first time I'm renting a studio,

00:06:11.600 --> 00:06:13.810
so I figured I should check out my options first.

00:06:13.970 --> 00:06:16.590
Yeah, totally! I definitely wanna go!

00:06:16.590 --> 00:06:17.720
I'm in!

00:06:17.720 --> 00:06:19.520
I'd love to come along, as well.

00:06:19.760 --> 00:06:23.020
Okay, then let's meet up at Shim-Misato Station this weekend.

00:06:23.020 --> 00:06:24.280
Okay!

00:06:25.200 --> 00:06:26.490
The place we're going...

00:06:27.400 --> 00:06:29.530
is a studio studio set up in an abandoned hospital.

00:06:31.370 --> 00:06:33.730
I never knew there were studios like this.

00:06:33.730 --> 00:06:36.200
This is totally my first time at an abandoned building.

00:06:36.200 --> 00:06:37.530
Mine, too!

00:06:37.530 --> 00:06:39.570
I was so excited for today...

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:42.310
I could barely fall asleep last night!

00:06:43.340 --> 00:06:46.510
Whoa, holy crap! This place rules!

00:06:47.490 --> 00:06:49.510
Oh, so it's this kind of place... You know...

00:06:49.170 --> 00:06:52.510
Dude, this place is way gloomier than I thought it'd be!
This is perfect for the abandoned hospital where Black Lily runs

00:06:52.440 --> 00:06:54.960
after she's defeated by Princess Daisy's straight right.

00:06:55.550 --> 00:06:56.640
Yeah.

00:06:56.640 --> 00:07:06.150
Mumble Mumble Mumble Mumble Mumble

00:06:57.010 --> 00:06:58.700
It's a depressing development,

00:06:58.700 --> 00:07:02.290
but I really like the scene where Shion starts to question herself.

00:07:03.040 --> 00:07:06.150
More importantly, I guess you really did watch the whole thing.

00:07:06.150 --> 00:07:07.520
Gojo-kun!

00:07:07.520 --> 00:07:09.380
We're gonna take a look upstairs!

00:07:09.380 --> 00:07:10.320
All right.
Let's go, Shinju-chan!

00:07:11.310 --> 00:07:12.420
Yes!

00:07:11.310 --> 00:07:13.520
It has a certain atmosphere, doesn't it?

00:07:17.900 --> 00:07:19.400
Is something wrong?

00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:21.540
N-No...

00:07:23.130 --> 00:07:24.920
Inui-san, could it be...

00:07:25.160 --> 00:07:27.590
Do places like this make you uncomfortable?

00:07:28.420 --> 00:07:30.410
Th-That's not true at all.

00:07:30.410 --> 00:07:31.840
Wh-What are you talking about?

00:07:31.840 --> 00:07:33.510
Come on! Let's go!

00:07:33.510 --> 00:07:34.970
Ah, so I was right...

00:07:35.370 --> 00:07:39.480
Hm... I mean, it's decent...

00:07:41.430 --> 00:07:44.010
Isn't it a bit too dark, though?

00:07:44.010 --> 00:07:46.100
We have a flash, so we'll be fine.

00:07:46.100 --> 00:07:47.770
You're, like, invincible!

00:07:48.010 --> 00:07:52.010
Flashes and reflectors can be used for outdoor shoots, too,

00:07:52.010 --> 00:07:53.500
so they're great to have.

00:07:53.500 --> 00:07:55.000
Even if it's sunny outside?

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:55.800
Yes!

00:08:01.880 --> 00:08:05.420
When it's nice outside, it's hard to keep your eyes open because it's too bright,

00:08:05.570 --> 00:08:07.700
so you make it your backlighting.

00:08:07.700 --> 00:08:10.200
Your skin will look nicer, too.

00:08:10.200 --> 00:08:14.220
But then, your face gets darker... Aha!

00:08:14.220 --> 00:08:16.780
So then you use the reflectors to brighten up your face!

00:08:16.780 --> 00:08:17.820
Yes!

00:08:17.820 --> 00:08:21.430
It makes wigs shine and improves your complexion, too.

00:08:21.430 --> 00:08:24.230
That's super amazing! I'll pass that along to Gojo-kun, too!

00:08:24.490 --> 00:08:26.060
Backlighting is the best.

00:08:26.060 --> 00:08:30.600
X-Ray Room Looks like it's gonna rain.

00:08:30.600 --> 00:08:31.680
Yes...

00:08:33.780 --> 00:08:37.160
Man, I'd love to do a shoot somewhere we can get some awesome pics.

00:08:37.160 --> 00:08:40.830
Actually, where do you guys go to take outdoor pics?

00:08:41.210 --> 00:08:43.050
Our yard...

00:08:47.180 --> 00:08:49.150
It's really coming down...

00:08:53.810 --> 00:08:55.390
Are you all right?

00:08:58.190 --> 00:08:59.180
Inui-san?

00:08:59.920 --> 00:09:02.490
I-I-I'm fine. I'm just a little tired.

00:09:02.490 --> 00:09:04.700
Yeah, she's not fine at all.

00:09:04.700 --> 00:09:06.350
Do you want to wait at the entrance?

00:09:06.520 --> 00:09:07.350
No!

00:09:08.840 --> 00:09:11.440
I'm going to cosplay Black Lily.

00:09:12.420 --> 00:09:14.900
I have to properly see what this place looks like...

00:09:14.900 --> 00:09:16.920
or I won't be able to get good pictures.

00:09:19.410 --> 00:09:23.140
I can go look for you, so please wait at the entrance.

00:09:23.810 --> 00:09:26.140
Hey! I'll do this myself!

00:09:26.140 --> 00:09:28.460
But you're pushing yourself, aren't you?

00:09:30.710 --> 00:09:32.970
Is there a reason?

00:09:36.520 --> 00:09:37.260
Do you...

00:09:38.250 --> 00:09:40.180
have any dreams for the future?

00:09:40.940 --> 00:09:41.960
Yes.

00:09:41.960 --> 00:09:44.020
To become a hina doll kashirashi.

00:09:44.020 --> 00:09:46.980
A job where you make the dolls' faces.

00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:49.350
That's a lovely dream.

00:09:49.930 --> 00:09:51.650
You'd better make sure it comes true.

00:09:52.530 --> 00:09:53.730
In my case...

00:09:57.550 --> 00:09:59.880
I wanted to become a magical girl.

00:10:02.360 --> 00:10:05.450
They're just so strong, dazzling, and cool,

00:10:05.450 --> 00:10:08.290
while wearing cute, frilly, little outfits.

00:10:09.330 --> 00:10:12.050
I looked up to magical girls so much when I was little.

00:10:12.050 --> 00:10:13.300
I was obsessed.

00:10:14.040 --> 00:10:17.710
I seriously wanted to become one when I got older.

00:10:18.640 --> 00:10:21.760
But once you get into elementary school, you figure it out.

00:10:21.760 --> 00:10:25.770
Flower Princess Blaze!!
It's all make-believe.

00:10:25.770 --> 00:10:29.170
And no matter how much I worked as hard like a magical girl, or prayed...

00:10:29.170 --> 00:10:32.250
I knew my dream would never come true.

00:10:33.530 --> 00:10:35.480
But then, when I was in middle school...

00:10:38.840 --> 00:10:41.300
I found out you could buy the outfits.

00:10:46.490 --> 00:10:50.210
I didn't have any prior knowledge, so I didn't even know how to style the wig.

00:10:50.550 --> 00:10:55.210
I didn't have any makeup on, and the outfit was too big for me.

00:10:56.310 --> 00:10:59.340
My first cosplay was just awful...

00:11:03.730 --> 00:11:07.220
But still... I was so, so happy.

00:11:08.040 --> 00:11:11.180
Even if I have to push myself, even if it's all make believe...

00:11:11.180 --> 00:11:13.760
I want to make my own dream come true.

00:11:18.140 --> 00:11:19.340
Inui-san.

00:11:19.340 --> 00:11:20.300
What?

00:11:20.810 --> 00:11:24.780
Why did you ask me to make such an important outfit for you?

00:11:25.140 --> 00:11:27.510
There are so many people better than me.

00:11:27.510 --> 00:11:29.910
You should ask someone else.

00:11:30.450 --> 00:11:32.020
Why did you choose me?

00:11:34.790 --> 00:11:38.210
When I saw Marin Kitagawa's photos...

00:11:38.560 --> 00:11:39.840
I was jealous.

00:11:42.090 --> 00:11:45.160
I know how pathetic being jealous is...

00:11:45.160 --> 00:11:48.600
But I was so horribly envious, I didn't know what to do.

00:11:49.610 --> 00:11:52.430
I thought, "I also want to wear an outfit made by this person."

00:11:53.170 --> 00:11:56.260
It had to be them.

00:11:59.690 --> 00:12:03.020
You're right. There are plenty of people who can make outfits.

00:12:03.020 --> 00:12:04.100
But...

00:12:05.060 --> 00:12:06.380
I'm sorry.

00:12:06.380 --> 00:12:08.710
I can't explain this very well.

00:12:08.710 --> 00:12:10.380
It's not exactly logical.

00:12:11.550 --> 00:12:13.500
I think the best way to describe it is...

00:12:14.130 --> 00:12:18.090
Seeing the outfit you made was love at first sight.

00:12:18.890 --> 00:12:23.030
To be honest, I'm surprised at myself for being jealous.

00:12:23.540 --> 00:12:27.350
But jealousy's something you feel about things that matter.

00:12:27.920 --> 00:12:29.930
Ain't they beauties?

00:12:30.100 --> 00:12:33.420
Your ol' gramps and his friends made these hina dolls.

00:12:33.420 --> 00:12:34.970
Ain't that amazing?

00:12:35.400 --> 00:12:37.440
Uh-huh. Wow...

00:12:38.610 --> 00:12:40.380
They're so pretty.

00:12:41.580 --> 00:12:44.950
She's the most beautiful thing in the world...

00:12:47.400 --> 00:12:49.790
The most beautiful in the world, eh?

00:12:51.380 --> 00:12:53.670
Out of all the doll shops out there,

00:12:53.670 --> 00:12:55.850
we're doin' everything we can to get these beauties

00:12:55.850 --> 00:12:58.950
to catch the eyes of customers, so they'll think these are the best there are.

00:12:58.950 --> 00:13:05.130
So hearin' you say they're the best makes your Gramps really happy.

00:13:05.560 --> 00:13:07.840
What does "catch the eyes" mean?

00:13:07.840 --> 00:13:12.400
Hm... How do I put this?

00:13:12.400 --> 00:13:15.190
Basically, we want people to experience love at first sight with 'em.

00:13:16.210 --> 00:13:17.380
Me, too...

00:13:19.240 --> 00:13:23.190
When I get older, I want to make hina dolls, too.

00:13:24.170 --> 00:13:26.050
I want to be like you, Gramps.

00:13:31.280 --> 00:13:36.330
With a little bit of practice, you'll be just like your Gramps.

00:13:43.240 --> 00:13:44.120
Uh?!

00:13:45.000 --> 00:13:48.010
Gramps... Uh, what? Wait, what?

00:13:48.010 --> 00:13:49.600
Why the heck are you crying?!

00:13:49.600 --> 00:13:50.640
What's your deal?

00:13:50.640 --> 00:13:54.020
What?! What?! Wh-What the heck is going on?!

00:13:54.020 --> 00:13:56.730
Say something, damn it!

00:13:58.180 --> 00:14:00.910
Fank you sho much...

00:14:01.910 --> 00:14:07.810
I just now... realized how happy Gramps was back then!

00:14:07.810 --> 00:14:10.210
I never imagined it was something like this.

00:14:10.730 --> 00:14:15.600
I promise... I absolutely promise that I'll do my best, so you'll...

00:14:13.680 --> 00:14:16.100
Sajuna Inui, age seventeen.

00:14:16.100 --> 00:14:18.840
Because she attends a private all-girls school,

00:14:18.840 --> 00:14:21.290
this was the first time she had a boy around her age

00:14:22.170 --> 00:14:23.840
hold her hand.

00:14:25.760 --> 00:14:28.430
Inui-san?! What's wrong, Inui-san?!
Gojo-kun?

00:14:28.140 --> 00:14:31.080
Dude, the thunder's crazy out there. You guys good?
Are you okay, Inui-san?!

00:14:31.970 --> 00:14:34.160
Final Exams We're done!

00:14:37.870 --> 00:14:38.840
Gojo-kun!

00:14:39.640 --> 00:14:40.860
Let's go to the beach!

00:14:41.770 --> 00:14:42.940
Like, right now!

00:14:44.230 --> 00:14:44.870
Huh?

00:14:47.760 --> 00:14:52.780
Swimming season hasn't started yet and there's no one around, so this is the best, am I right?

00:14:58.690 --> 00:15:00.870
We've basically got the whole place to ourselves.

00:15:01.300 --> 00:15:03.310
We're actually here...

00:15:05.400 --> 00:15:08.560
Um... Did we come here today to take some photos?

00:15:09.510 --> 00:15:13.320
During our location hunt, you said you wanted to try taking some backlit photos.

00:15:13.320 --> 00:15:14.800
