Right.

00:15:25.700 --> 00:15:27.400
And it's July, right?

00:15:27.740 --> 00:15:29.190
And it's summer, right?

00:15:30.140 --> 00:15:31.450
"We headin' to the beach!"

00:15:32.790 --> 00:15:33.810
That's all.

00:15:34.510 --> 00:15:37.440
Doesn't going to the beach in your uniform just scream the power of youth?!

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:39.420
This is epic!

00:15:40.800 --> 00:15:43.830
That's right... This is how Kitagawa-san is...

00:15:44.050 --> 00:15:45.760
She's incredibly proactive...

00:15:45.760 --> 00:15:47.420
Definitely eating from this place again.

00:15:47.420 --> 00:15:49.690
Gojo-kun, could you give me some fries?

00:15:49.690 --> 00:15:50.470
Sure...

00:15:50.780 --> 00:15:52.760
French fries, French fries, yay!

00:15:53.620 --> 00:15:55.290
Ahh... Huh?!

00:15:57.480 --> 00:15:58.220
Wait...

00:15:59.160 --> 00:16:00.980
Hey!

00:16:00.980 --> 00:16:04.190
My burger!

00:16:08.800 --> 00:16:10.880
That bird's still following us.

00:16:10.880 --> 00:16:13.440
Should we go somewhere else to eat?

00:16:13.440 --> 00:16:15.780
Nah, we came all the way here.

00:16:16.110 --> 00:16:18.280
You wanna have bubble tea while looking at the ocean?

00:16:18.640 --> 00:16:21.250
We even brought a mat with us.

00:16:21.480 --> 00:16:24.300
We can figure out what to do if that bird steals our food again later.

00:16:29.450 --> 00:16:30.540
All right.

00:16:31.060 --> 00:16:32.260
Gojo-kun?

00:16:33.450 --> 00:16:36.030
Please give up on the French fries!

00:16:39.490 --> 00:16:42.020
Let's make a break for it!

00:16:42.020 --> 00:16:44.150
We still have one more burger!

00:16:48.820 --> 00:16:51.870
Oh, no. That was probably littering...

00:16:53.210 --> 00:16:54.110
Let's go!

00:16:55.920 --> 00:16:58.130
Bye-bye, Mr. Hambirdglar!

00:17:01.540 --> 00:17:02.350
Here you go.

00:17:02.810 --> 00:17:04.610
But that's yours, Gojo-kun. Are you sure?

00:17:04.610 --> 00:17:05.490
Yes.

00:17:06.630 --> 00:17:07.870
Thank you...

00:17:12.500 --> 00:17:13.260
Mm.

00:17:14.540 --> 00:17:15.830
It's super good.

00:17:16.560 --> 00:17:17.770
Thank you.

00:17:19.470 --> 00:17:22.770
I never knew whitebait was good on burgers.

00:17:22.770 --> 00:17:23.870
I know, right?

00:17:29.290 --> 00:17:31.060
Yo, this bubble tea is bomb.

00:17:31.060 --> 00:17:32.830
Want a sip, Gojo-kun?

00:17:32.830 --> 00:17:33.330
Huh?

00:17:33.330 --> 00:17:35.250
No, that's all right.

00:17:35.250 --> 00:17:36.400
Yeah?

00:17:46.820 --> 00:17:49.530
The breeze feels so nice.

00:17:51.050 --> 00:17:52.500
Yes.

00:17:54.700 --> 00:17:57.380
All right, I'm going in.

00:17:57.880 --> 00:17:59.140
Hang onto this for me.

00:17:59.140 --> 00:18:00.970
Huh? Wait, you're going to swim?

00:18:01.720 --> 00:18:04.100
'Course not! I'm just gonna soak my feet!

00:18:04.320 --> 00:18:06.570
I decided this spur-of-the-moment, so I didn't bring a swimsuit, either!

00:18:06.570 --> 00:18:09.230
Here I go!

00:18:09.980 --> 00:18:13.120
It's so cold! It feels awesome!

00:18:13.120 --> 00:18:14.800
What a free spirit...

00:18:18.060 --> 00:18:18.990
Oh, man!

00:18:19.730 --> 00:18:22.580
Dude! I caught some seaweed!

00:18:22.580 --> 00:18:24.740
Do you see this stuff? It's hilarious!

00:18:25.000 --> 00:18:27.470
Look, Gojo-kun, look!

00:18:28.010 --> 00:18:31.620
Oh, I am... Gojo-kun, get in here, my dude!

00:18:31.620 --> 00:18:34.350
It's like, the best thing ever!

00:18:34.350 --> 00:18:35.800
Uh, okay!

00:18:40.790 --> 00:18:42.430
Hurry, hurry!

00:18:43.020 --> 00:18:45.270
One moment... please.

00:18:58.900 --> 00:18:59.960
Whoa, a wave.

00:18:59.960 --> 00:19:01.180
It really is cold.

00:19:01.180 --> 00:19:02.740
Wow...

00:19:03.110 --> 00:19:06.480
Um, my feet seem to be sinking into the sand?!

00:19:06.480 --> 00:19:08.300
You're way too freaked out.

00:19:08.300 --> 00:19:10.020
It's like you've never been to the beach.

00:19:10.020 --> 00:19:12.160
Uh, it is... Huh?

00:19:12.840 --> 00:19:14.490
Wait, really?

00:19:14.490 --> 00:19:17.290
No way... Then again, I guess Saitama's pretty landlocked.

00:19:17.290 --> 00:19:20.260
Er, that's not it, exactly.

00:19:21.450 --> 00:19:24.850
Ever since I was little, the way I had fun was staring at hina dolls

00:19:25.750 --> 00:19:29.880
and practicing how to draw the faces.

00:19:31.380 --> 00:19:35.230
That's all I ever did, so I never thought of doing anything else.

00:19:37.950 --> 00:19:40.720
As a result, there are a lot of places I've never been.

00:19:42.690 --> 00:19:47.470
Gramps told me that I should observe a lot of things.

00:19:48.460 --> 00:19:49.870
He was right.

00:19:50.420 --> 00:19:52.850
This is nothing like what I've seen on TV or in photos.

00:19:55.940 --> 00:19:58.260
The beach is very nice.

00:20:00.510 --> 00:20:01.700
It's beautiful.

00:20:11.650 --> 00:20:14.520
Then... we should go to all sorts of places together!

00:20:16.120 --> 00:20:18.570
I-It's almost summer vacation, right?

00:20:18.570 --> 00:20:21.120
I'll invite you everywhere!

00:20:21.780 --> 00:20:25.620
So let's go... J-Just the two of us!

00:20:27.280 --> 00:20:28.580
Are you sure?

00:20:28.880 --> 00:20:30.660
I would love to!

00:20:30.660 --> 00:20:31.910
That makes me really happy.

00:20:35.520 --> 00:20:39.510
Y-You know... I'm getting a little thirsty...

00:20:39.510 --> 00:20:41.180
I'm gonna have some more tea.

00:20:41.790 --> 00:20:42.620
Okay.

00:20:49.250 --> 00:20:52.730
I-I totally just blurted, "Just the two of us!"

00:20:54.170 --> 00:20:55.730
Oh, my god! Oh my freakin' God! Ohmigod!

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:59.920
I'd be so embarrassed if he saw how red my face was! Like, I'd literally die!

00:21:00.480 --> 00:21:01.440
Hold up.

00:21:01.710 --> 00:21:04.420
This means I'm gonna see him all summer break.

00:21:04.420 --> 00:21:07.620
Whoa, I literally can't... Holy crap.

00:21:28.020 --> 00:21:29.410
Wow...

00:21:30.780 --> 00:21:32.100
She wasn't joking.

00:21:33.890 --> 00:21:35.550
He looks super amazing.

00:21:40.480 --> 00:21:41.400
Uh, dude?!

00:21:41.580 --> 00:21:42.850
Gojo-kun?!

00:21:43.680 --> 00:21:46.910
My body... My whole body's covered in seaweed!

00:21:46.910 --> 00:21:49.290
It's all slippery! And slimy!

00:21:50.160 --> 00:21:52.300
Gojo-kun, are you okay?!

00:21:52.300 --> 00:21:53.660
What the heck are you doing?!

00:21:53.660 --> 00:21:57.670
I-I tried to go a bit further, and I slipped on some seaweed.

00:21:58.250 --> 00:22:00.170
You're totally soaked!

00:22:00.170 --> 00:22:02.200
Oh, no... How can I go home like this?

00:22:02.200 --> 00:22:04.480
Oh, you'll dry off by then... I think!

00:23:34.970 --> 00:23:39.980
Episode 9
Because There Was a Lot That I Saw in That Photo

00:23:35.280 --> 00:23:36.280
Next time!